
character barista
  name: Alex

beat Menu
  barista: What'll it be?

  choice
    Espresso -> MakeEspresso
    Latte -> MakeLatte
    Leave -> Goodbye

beat MakeEspresso
  barista: One espresso, coming right up!

beat MakeLatte
  barista: One latte, extra foam!

beat Goodbye
  barista: See you next time!

